Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.35,0:34:18.32,Default8,,0,0,0,,Um, Pinkie Pie, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.35,0:34:20.30,Default8,,0,0,0,,Putting marshmallows in my lantern.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.30,0:34:23.72,Default8,,0,0,0,,Then when we light them, mine will be beautiful and delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.90,0:34:28.36,Default8,,0,0,0,,Hey, Twilight, why aren't you with everyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.36,0:34:32.39,Default8,,0,0,0,,Sunset said something at camp is causing the other girls to get new magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.39,0:34:34.45,Default8,,0,0,0,,I think it's Midnight Sparkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.45,0:34:35.90,Default8,,0,0,0,,She's still part of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.90,0:34:37.03,Default8,,0,0,0,,I can feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.03,0:34:39.85,Default8,,0,0,0,,And I think her magic is infecting my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.85,0:34:41.03,Default8,,0,0,0,,What are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.47,0:34:43.03,Default8,,0,0,0,,I don't know what I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.50,0:34:45.08,Default8,,0,0,0,,Okay, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.08,0:34:48.42,Default8,,0,0,0,,It's time to watch your lanterns fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.45,0:34:56.13,Default8,,0,0,0,,Hey, cool lantern!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.33,0:34:58.13,Default8,,0,0,0,,Mine's my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.31,0:35:07.77,Default8,,0,0,0,,Uh, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.77,0:35:08.73,Default8,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.73,0:35:10.90,Default8,,0,0,0,,You don't seem like yourself tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.02,0:35:19.82,Default8,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.82,0:35:22.24,Default8,,0,0,0,,And... go!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.87,0:35:30.33,Default8,,0,0,0,,Aw! Oh well!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.33,0:35:31.54,Default8,,0,0,0,,Now I get to eat it! 
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.50,0:35:35.84,Default8,,0,0,0,,Yep, Beautiful and delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.56,0:35:51.35,Default8,,0,0,0,,Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.61,0:35:56.94,Default8,,0,0,0,,Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.15,0:35:59.78,Default8,,0,0,0,,Where is she going?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.83,0:36:06.99,Default8,,0,0,0,,Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.29,0:36:11.00,Default8,,0,0,0,,What are you doing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.00,0:36:14.13,Default8,,0,0,0,,We're... we're meeting a cab to take us home.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.43,0:36:17.04,Default8,,0,0,0,,She thought you'd talk her out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.04,0:36:18.38,Default8,,0,0,0,,Because I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.38,0:36:20.46,Default8,,0,0,0,,Twilight, you can't leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.34,0:36:24.55,Default8,,0,0,0,,You don't think it was the spirit, do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.10,0:36:27.39,Default8,,0,0,0,,No, it was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.39,0:36:29.47,Default8,,0,0,0,,I think it's Midnight Sparkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.47,0:36:30.73,Default8,,0,0,0,,She's still part of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.73,0:36:31.85,Default8,,0,0,0,,I can feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.85,0:36:34.56,Default8,,0,0,0,,And I think her magic is infecting my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.77,0:36:40.32,Default8,,0,0,0,,Twilight, there's no Midnight Sparkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.32,0:36:41.74,Default8,,0,0,0,,There's only you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.90,0:36:43.61,Default8,,0,0,0,,How did you know what I was thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.99,0:36:46.53,Default8,,0,0,0,,When I touched your hand, I can see things.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.53,0:36:48.45,Default8,,0,0,0,,I can understand why you were leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.62,0:36:50.95,Default8,,0,0,0,,My new magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.45,0:36:52.80,Default8,,0,0,0,,This is my new magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.80,0:36:54.16,Default8,,0,0,0,,This is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.16,0:36:55.42,Default8,,0,0,0,,No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.42,0:36:57.00,Default8,,0,0,0,,I'm infecting you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.00,0:37:00.26,Default8,,0,0,0,,Twilight, you have to stop looking at this as a bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.26,0:37:01.65,Default8,,0,0,0,,Easy for you to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.65,0:37:03.68,Default8,,0,0,0,,Magic turned you into something beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.90,0:37:05.60,Default8,,0,0,0,,The last time I tried to use it,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.60,0:37:07.20,Default8,,0,0,0,,it turned me into a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.64,0:37:10.00,Default8,,0,0,0,,I'm just so afraid it's gonna happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.12,0:37:13.71,Default8,,0,0,0,,Yes, last time I turned into something amazing,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.71,0:37:16.18,Default8,,0,0,0,,but I've let magic turn me into a monster, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.60,0:37:20.12,Default8,,0,0,0,,So if anyone understands what you're going through, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.32,0:37:22.19,Default8,,0,0,0,,I can help you, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.19,0:37:24.39,Default8,,0,0,0,,And the rest of our friends can be there for you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.68,0:37:26.42,Default8,,0,0,0,,But not if you run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.69,0:37:29.46,Default8,,0,0,0,,I'll stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.46,0:37:31.43,Default8,,0,0,0,,I still don't think this is a good idea for me
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.43,0:37:33.45,Default8,,0,0,0,,to be near the rest of our friends right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.68,0:37:35.68,Default8,,0,0,0,,Not until we know why this is happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.72,0:37:37.59,Default8,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.75,0:37:39.99,Default8,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.80,0:37:45.00,Default8,,0,0,0,,Wait. Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.84,0:37:46.69,Default8,,0,0,0,,Timber?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.69,0:37:48.69,Default8,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad it's just you!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.69,0:37:50.69,Default8,,0,0,0,,Wait, what are you doing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.69,0:37:51.96,Default8,,0,0,0,,With an axe?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.06,0:37:55.48,Default8,,0,0,0,,I was chopping down firewood.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.55,0:37:57.42,Default8,,0,0,0,,In the middle of the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.42,0:37:59.52,Default8,,0,0,0,,We needed more for tomorrow night's campfire.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.89,0:38:02.09,Default8,,0,0,0,,And if I didn't take care of it tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.09,0:38:05.09,Default8,,0,0,0,,it would be one more thing Gloriosa would add to her list.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.09,0:38:07.09,Default8,,0,0,0,,I've got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.32,0:38:09.45,Default8,,0,0,0,,What about you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.45,0:38:12.60,Default8,,0,0,0,,Why are you hanging out in the woods in the middle of the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.19,0:38:14.95,Default8,,0,0,0,,Oh, I was sleepwalking.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.95,0:38:17.44,Default8,,0,0,0,,Twilight found me and was bringing me back to camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.44,0:38:18.34,Default8,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.34,0:38:20.91,Default8,,0,0,0,,Come on, I'll walk you guys back.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.91,0:38:25.30,Default8,,0,0,0,,I'll protect you from Gaia Everfree!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.30,0:38:29.65,Default8,,0,0,0,,Everfree! Everfree!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.36,0:38:31.29,Default8,,0,0,0,,Come on,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.29,0:38:35.23,Default8,,0,0,0,,that's obviously just a spooky story you made up to tell around the campfire.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.23,0:38:36.00,Default8,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.30,0:38:37.41,Default8,,0,0,0,,It's legit.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.41,0:38:39.75,Default8,,0,0,0,,How else would you explain what happened at the docks?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.75,0:38:42.10,Default8,,0,0,0,,And that weird thing when the earth shook?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.58,0:38:45.46,Default8,,0,0,0,,Uh, come on, I know a shortcut back to the tents.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.12,0:38:53.79,Default8,,0,0,0,,Legit, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.82,0:38:57.21,Default8,,0,0,0,,I think we just found our "Gaia Everfree".
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.21,0:39:00.48,Default8,,0,0,0,,But why would he work so hard to make us think she was real?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.48,0:39:01.70,Default8,,0,0,0,,You heard what he said
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.70,0:39:03.85,Default8,,0,0,0,,about wishing his sister would sell this camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.85,0:39:05.85,Default8,,0,0,0,,If nobody wants to come here,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.85,0:39:08.72,Default8,,0,0,0,,because it's home to some angry ancient nature spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.72,0:39:10.72,Default8,,0,0,0,,it sure would help his cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.90,0:39:12.70,Default8,,0,0,0,,We should tell Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.70,0:39:13.77,Default8,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.77,0:39:16.12,Default8,,0,0,0,,She's obviously going on through a lot right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.74,0:39:18.93,Default8,,0,0,0,,We should probably be a hundred percent sure
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.93,0:39:21.58,Default8,,0,0,0,,before we tell her the guy she likes is a jerk
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.58,0:39:23.58,Default8,,0,0,0,,who's trying to run everybody out of camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.58,0:39:24.90,Default8,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.58,0:39:36.34,Default8,,0,0,0,,Phew!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.45,0:39:40.83,Default8,,0,0,0,,Uh, you gonna give us a hand here, Rarity?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.83,0:39:42.05,Default8,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'd love to,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.05,0:39:44.26,Default8,,0,0,0,,but I really need to get the stitching on this poncho done
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.26,0:39:46.26,Default8,,0,0,0,,before it's going to make it into the camp fashion show.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.26,0:39:48.34,Default8,,0,0,0,,Though at the pace you two are moving,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.34,0:39:50.75,Default8,,0,0,0,,I don't know that the runway will ever be finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.75,0:39:53.26,Default8,,0,0,0,,The dock is our gift to the camp
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.26,0:39:54.89,Default8,,0,0,0,,and it's gonna get finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.51,0:39:58.69,Default8,,0,0,0,,That is if Rainbow Dash would hurry up and bring me more wood.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.69,0:40:00.90,Default8,,0,0,0,,Oh, I can't go any faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.90,0:40:02.90,Default8,,0,0,0,,I don't want to end up in the woods again.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.19,0:40:04.83,Default8,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.85,0:40:06.20,Default8,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.32,0:40:13.87,Default8,,0,0,0,,I know I said we should try to forget all about this new magic business,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.87,0:40:15.08,Default8,,0,0,0,,but I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.97,0:40:18.10,Default8,,0,0,0,,What if I hammer the board into splinters?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.52,0:40:21.54,Default8,,0,0,0,,Aw, shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.52,0:40:22.69,Default8,,0,0,0,,I'm all out of nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.69,0:40:24.38,Default8,,0,0,0,,Oh, here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.75,0:40:26.50,Default8,,0,0,0,,Pinkie, no! 
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.97,0:40:34.22,Default8,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.22,0:40:37.26,Default8,,0,0,0,,Ohhh, did you think that nails would explode like the sprinkles?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.26,0:40:39.60,Default8,,0,0,0,,Wow! Glad that didn't happen, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.94,0:40:41.90,Default8,,0,0,0,,Sorry, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.90,0:40:43.19,Default8,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.19,0:40:45.55,Default8,,0,0,0,,And I don't know how to control this.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.55,0:40:46.73,Default8,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.73,0:40:48.73,Default8,,0,0,0,,Oh, none of us do.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.73,0:40:51.65,Default8,,0,0,0,,Which is why we shouldn't pretend this isn't happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.11,0:40:53.36,Default8,,0,0,0,,Do you have them now, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.36,0:40:54.70,Default8,,0,0,0,,It's started last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.70,0:40:55.87,Default8,,0,0,0,,When I touch people,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.87,0:40:58.74,Default8,,0,0,0,,it's like I can feel what they're feeling and see their memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.74,0:41:02.00,Default8,,0,0,0,,Oooh, fancy! Try me, try me!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.63,0:41:08.21,Default8,,0,0,0,,La-la-la-la. Ooh, taffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.97,0:41:12.89,Default8,,0,0,0,,That explains so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.89,0:41:13.80,Default8,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.50,0:41:17.10,Default8,,0,0,0,,Girls, we can't just brush these powers aside
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.10,0:41:19.98,Default8,,0,0,0,,because it doesn't seem like the ideal time to get them.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.52,0:41:24.94,Default8,,0,0,0,,What if it turns out that they could actually make things better?
